{"title_page": "Sora/Koe", "text_new": "{{Infobox song\n| name       = Sora/Koe\n| cover      =\n| alt        =\n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[Every Little Thing (band)|Every Little Thing]]\n| album      = [[Ordinary (Every Little Thing album)|ORDINARY]]\n| released   = July 13, 2011\n| format     = [[CD single]]\n| recorded   = 2011\n| studio     =\n| venue      =\n| genre      = [[J-pop]]\n| length     =\n| label      = [[Avex Group|Avex Trax]]\n| composer   =\n| lyricist   =\n| producer   =\n| prev_title = [[Moon (Every Little Thing song)|Moon]]\n| prev_year  = 2011\n| next_title = [[Ai ga Aru]]\n| next_year  = 2011\n}}\n\n{{nihongo|\"'''Sora/Koe'''\"|\u5b99 -\u305d\u3089-/\u97ff -\u3053\u3048-||lit. Air/Voice}} is the 42nd single of the Japanese pop group [[Every Little Thing (band)|Every Little Thing]], released on July 13, 2011. The single contains two songs: \"Sora\" and its B-side, \"Koe\". Both songs are used as the ending theme for the ''[[Pok\u00e9mon]]'' movie ''[[Victini and the Black Hero: Zekrom and Victini and the White Hero: Reshiram]]''.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.avexnet.or.jp/elt/news/110413.html|title=\u3010\u5287\u5834\u7248\u30dd\u30b1\u30c3\u30c8\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc \u30d9\u30b9\u30c8\u30a6\u30a4\u30c3\u30b7\u30e5\u300c\u30d3\u30af\u30c6\u30a3\u30cb\u3068\u9ed2\u304d\u82f1\u96c4 \u30bc\u30af\u30ed\u30e0\u300d\u300c\u30d3\u30af\u30c6\u30a3\u30cb\u3068\u767d\u304d\u82f1\u96c4 \u30ec\u30b7\u30e9\u30e0\u300d\u3011\u3067Every Little Thing\u304c\u6b4c\u3046\u300c\u5b99 -\u305d\u3089-\u300d\u304c\u4e3b\u984c\u6b4c\u3068\u3057\u3066\u6c7a\u5b9a\uff01\uff01|date=2011-04-13|accessdate=2011-04-14|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110416083407/http://www.avexnet.or.jp/elt/news/110413.html|archivedate=2011-04-16}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.avexnet.or.jp/elt/news/110516_01.html|title=2011\u5e747\u670813\u65e5\u3000\u30cb\u30e5\u30fc\u30b7\u30f3\u30b0\u30eb\u767a\u58f2\u6c7a\u5b9a\uff01\uff01 \u203b\u7