{"title_page": "Why", "text_new": "{{selfref|See also: [[Wikipedia:WHY (disambiguation)|Wikipedia:WHY]]}}\n{{Wiktionary|why}}\n'''Why''' may refer to:\n\n* [[Causality]], a consequential relationship between two events\n* [[Reason (argument)]], a premise in support of an argument, for what reason or purpose\n* [[Grounding (metaphysics)]], a topic in metaphysics regarding how things exist in virtue of more fundamental things.\n* Why?, one of the [[Five Ws]] used in journalism\n\n{{TOC right|limit=3}}\n== Music ==\n=== Artists ===\n* [[Why? (American band)]], a hip hop / indie rock band formed in Oakland, California, in 2004\n** [[Yoni Wolf]], formerly known by the stage name Why?\n* Why?, a 1990s UK folk band, two members of which later formed [[Quench (band)|Quench]] in 2001\n* [[Why (Canadian band)]], a rock band formed in Winnipeg, Manitoba, in 1993\n\n=== Albums ===\n* [[Why? (Discharge album)|''Why?'' (Discharge album)]]\n* [[Why? (Ginger Baker album)|''Why?'' (Ginger Baker album)]]\n* [[Why? (Jacob Whitesides album)|''Why?'' (Jacob Whitesides album)]]\n* [[Why (Prudence Liew album)|''Why'' (Prudence Liew album)]]\n* [[Why? (They Might Be Giants album)|''Why?'' (They Might Be Giants album)]]\n* [[Why (Taeyeon EP)|''Why'' (Taeyeon EP)]]\n* [[Why (Baby V.O.X)|''Why'' (Baby V.O.X)]]\n* ''Why'', by [[Moahni Moahna]]\n\n=== Songs ===\n* [[Why (3T song)|\"Why\" (3T song)]], featuring Michael Jackson\n* [[Why (Andy Gibb song)|\"Why\" (Andy Gibb song)]]\n* [[Why (Annie Lennox song)|\"Why\" (Annie Lennox song)]], covered by DJ Sammy, Kelly Clarkson, Lara Fabian, Allison Crowe, and others\n* [[Why? (Bronski Beat song)|\"Why?\" (Bronski Beat song)]]\n* [[Why (The Byrds song)|\"Why\" (The Byrds song)]], B-side to the single \"Eight Miles High\"\n* [[Why (Carly Simon song)|\"Why\" (Carly Simon song)]]\n* [[Why (Cathy Dennis song)|\"Why\" (Cathy Dennis song)]]\n* [[Why (Frankie Avalon song)|\"Why\" (Frankie Avalon song)]], covered by Anthony Newley and by Donny Osmond\n* [[Why (Gabrielle song)|\"Why\" (Gabrielle song)]]\n* [[Why? (Geir R\u00f6nning song)|\"Why?\" (Geir R\u00f6nning song)]]\n* [[Why (Glamma Kid song)|\"Why\" (Glamma Kid song)]]\n* [[Why (Godsmack song)|\"Why\" (Godsmack song)]]\n* [[Why (Jadakiss song)|\"Why\" (Jadakiss song)]]\n* [[Why (Jason Aldean song)|\"Why\" (Jason Aldean song)]]\n* [[Why (Jieqiong song)|\"Why\" (Jieqiong song)]]\n* [[Why (Lionel Richie song)|\"Why\" (Lionel Richie song)]]\n* [[Why? (Marika Gombitov\u00e1 song)|\"Why?\" (Marika Gombitov\u00e1 song)]]\n* [[Why (Mary J. Blige song)|\"Why\" (Mary J. Blige song)]], featuring Rick Ross\n* [[Why (Miliyah Kato song)|\"Why\" (Miliyah Kato song)]]\n* [[Why? (Mis-Teeq song)|\"Why?\" (Mis-Teeq song)]]\n* [[Why (Rascal Flatts song)|\"Why\" (Rascal Flatts song)]]\n* [[Why (Sabrina Carpenter song)|\"Why\" (Sabrina Carpenter song)]]\n* [[Why (Sonique song)|\"Why\" (Sonique song)]]\n* [[Why (Tony Sheridan song)|\"Why\" (Tony Sheridan song)]], with The Beatles\n* \"[[Why (Must We Fall in Love)]]\", a song by Diana Ross & The Supremes\n* \"[[Why, Why, Why]]\", a song by Billy Currington\n* \"Why\", by 4Minute from ''[[Best of 4Minute]]''\n* \"Why\", by Air Supply from ''[[Mumbo Jumbo (album)|Mumbo Jumbo]]''\n* \"Why?\", by Amin\u00e9 from ''[[OnePointFive]]''\n* \"Why\", by Antique from ''[[Die for You (Antique album)|Die for You]]''\n* \"Why\", by Average White Band from ''[[Cut the Cake (album)|Cut the Cake]]''\n* \"Why\" by Avril Lavigne, B-side to the single \"[[Complicated (Avril Lavigne song)|Complicated]]\"\n* \"Why\", by Ayaka from the single [[Clap & Love/Why|\"Clap & Love\"/\"Why\"]] and the theme song of the PSP game ''Crisis Core: Final Fantasy VII''\n* \"Why\", by Bazzi from ''[[Cosmic (album)|Cosmic]]''\n* \"Why\", by Basshunter from ''[[Bass Generation]]''\n* \"Why\", by Busted from ''[[A Present for Everyone]]''\n* \"Why, Pt. 2\", by Collective Soul from ''[[Blender (Collective Soul album)|Blender]]''\n* \"Why?\", by Des'ree from ''[[Dream Soldier]]'